    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Good morning...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day8_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Good morning, Nana. You seem a bit down today?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Um... actually... all weekend, I was thinking about you, sensei...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day8_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "About me?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Yes... since Saturday night, my body has been so hot...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day8_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway_openmouth",
      "text": "I tried... um... touching myself... but it wasn't satisfying at all...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day8_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "(She masturbated... but still couldn't be satisfied. That's perfect.)"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "It seems like... it has to be your hands, sensei...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day8_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "What's happening to my body...?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day8_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "That's... because your body has completely memorized my treatment, Nana."
